sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Manager
  participant Editor as Restaurant Editor
  participant Confirm as confirmInfo()
  participant Gateway as restaurant-write stage/commit
  participant DB as restaurants + change_logs

  Manager->>Editor: Complete menu + brand verification
  Manager->>Editor: Click final Confirm information is up-to-date
  Editor->>Confirm: confirmInfo(photos)
  Confirm->>Gateway: Stage operation type CONFIRM_INFO
  Gateway-->>Confirm: batchId
  Confirm->>Gateway: Commit staged batch
  Gateway->>DB: Persist confirmation + change log
  DB-->>Gateway: Write success
  Gateway-->>Editor: Commit payload
  Editor-->>Manager: Success toast + updated due state

  alt Photos missing or payload invalid
    Confirm-->>Editor: Validation error
    Editor-->>Manager: Show confirmation error
  end
